OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with light and patchy rain.
OL,7,FThe rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fcloudy with rain turning showery and
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy. Southwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds becoming strong to gale force.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy at first with
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy rain clearing east.
OL,14,FThen turning brighter with a few
OL,15,Fscattered showers. Strong to near gale
OL,16,Fforce southwesterly winds soon veer
OL,17,Fnorthwesterly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
