OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells on Sunday with a few
OL,7,Fshowers. Dry start Monday, then
OL,8,Fturning fairly unsettled and
OL,9,Fchangeable later Monday into Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith the risk of rain or showers.
